A COMMUNITY event is being held for the Barrhead South Master- plan consultation. Event to focus on council's masterplan A COMMUNITY event is being held for the Barrhead South Master- plan consultation.The event, staged by East Renfrewshire Council's planning service, is to take place in the foyer of the Barr-head Health Centre on November 13, between 1pm and 5.30pm.The plan sets out the council's vision for the delivery of the Barr-head South strategic development area. 